That's the truth right there.  All y'all &quot;Pvp sounds like fun but I don't wanna leave all my gear and my stuff!!&quot; people should read that again.  Yeah eq pvp isn't perfect.  No pvp is perfect.<br>
<br>
Our population is somewhere around 300-800 off/prime.  SZ's population changes everyday as new people join and old people leave.  I think one of the best parts is making a name for yourself.  The community is so small that everyone knows everyone else.  A newt rogue isn't just some faceless guy from another guild, he's the guy that backstabbed me for double 300's in a kith forest epic fight.  <br>
<br>
our message board is pretty crappy, populated by people that no longer play sz, and make the same type of remarks I've seen in this thread, every day.  enh~<br>
