Evil team controls pretty much any zone they want when they want.<br>
<br>
Evil has more players than any other team so it is more likely to find a group.<br>
<br>
Organization does not occur in the lower levels on Sullon Zek very often, the most organized guilds (55+) are: Hate, Ruin, and Defilers.  Da Bashin Iggles are an organized guild who mostly pvp and aren't really into high end content, but they do plane raids and such.<br>
<br>
I played on TZ since a few months after release, as soon as Sullon came out I played full time and haven't looked back.<br>
<br>
The whining and crying that occurs on most blue/pink servers only gets you killed on Sullon.<br>
<br>
Sure it has it's share of idiots, but what server doesn't really?<br>
<br>
